               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image 1r and 2l: scrawls. Images 2r-147r: Psalter, poorly copied. The midpoint is marked with a cross in the right margin (image 59l). Psalm 151 is the long version. Song of Songs is the common edition. Praises of Mary begins with Monday and culminates on Sunday. Illuminations are added recently over text. Images 148r-149l: An asmat prayer, text is effaced. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
